## SSL/TLS Configuration

### Let's Encrypt (Free SSL)

```bash
# Install certbot
sudo apt install certbot python3-certbot-nginx

# Obtain certificate
sudo certbot --nginx -d {{DOMAIN_NAME}}

# Auto-renewal (runs twice daily)
sudo systemctl enable certbot.timer
```

