## Rollback Strategy

### Quick Rollback

**Heroku:**
```bash
heroku rollback
```

**Docker:**
```bash
docker-compose down
docker-compose up -d <previous-image-tag>
```

**PM2:**
```bash
pm2 stop {{PROJECT_NAME}}
git checkout <previous-commit>
{{PACKAGE_MANAGER}} install
{{BUILD_COMMAND}}
pm2 restart {{PROJECT_NAME}}
```

